Package: GPlinksR
Type: Package
Title: Building Gene–Peak Network for ATAC–RNA Integration
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Xinran", "Wang", email = "xwang210@usc.edu", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Kelly", "Street", email = "kelly.street@usc.edu", role = "ctb"))
Description: GPlinksR provides a simple interface to build gene–peak networks 
    by integrating enhancer, promoter, and proximity-based (closest-gene) 
    mapping using public enhancer–gene link data from PANTHER/AnnoQ.
